Argued and submitted April 21, In the Matter of the Marriage of Tracey Anne COCKRELL, Respondent, and Samuel Preston COCKRELL, Appellant. (C982034DR; CA A106929) 1 P3d 513 Robert M. Hildum argued the cause for appellant. With him on the brief were Brian J. Sunderland, and Aunderland & Associates. PER CURIAM

vacated and remanded in part; otherwise affirmed May 31, 2000

Robert T. Scherzer argued the cause and filed the brief for respondent.

Before Edmonds, Presiding Judge, and Armstrong and Kistler, Judges.
